              </h4>
            </li>
            <li class="slider__slide">
              <img class="post-carousel__image" src="../images/novosibirsk.jpg" alt="Novosibirsk">
              <h4 class="post-carousel__image-caption">
                Novosibirsk, oblast (region), south-central Russia, in western Siberia.
              </h4>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <button class="slider__button slider__button_type_prev" type="button"></button>
